",["$r","Note",null,{"children":[["$r","p",null,{"children":["We recommend using ",["$r","code",null,{"children":"act"}]," with ",["$r","code",null,{"children":"await"}]," and an ",["$r","code",null,{"children":"async"}]," function. Although the sync version works in many cases, it doesn’t work in all cases and due to the way React schedules updates internally, it’s difficult to predict when you can use the sync version."]}],["$r","p",null,{"children":"We will deprecate and remove the sync version in the future."}]]}],"
